title: Sujal Sarangdhar
summary: Sujal Sarangdhar is an aspiring Software Developer with experience in Python, Django, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. He has worked on full-stack applications, integrated ML models, and developed projects spanning cab booking systems, IoT-enabled tracking, and machine learning classification models. Sujal holds an MCA degree from K.K. Wagh Institute Of Engg. Education And Research and possesses certifications in AWS Cloud Practitioner and Core Java. He is proficient in various programming languages, tools, and databases, with a strong grasp of AI/ML concepts.

content.title: Software Developer | Tega IT Solutions PVT. LTD.

Integrated ML models and optimized backend performance.
